OL,7,FBritish Gas owner Centrica, EG Group
OL,8,Fand Holland & Barrett are among the
OL,9,Flatest firms to be named by the
OL,10,FGovernment for failing to pay some of
OL,11,Ftheir staff the minimum wage.
OL,13,FThe Department for Business and Trade
OL,14,F(DBT) released a list of 491 employers
OL,15,Fthat underpaid workers over several
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,18,FThey will pay a fine amounting to a
OL,19,Fcombined #10.2 million as a result of
OL,20,Fbreaking the rules.
