OL,7,FIt means pay for some staff fell short
OL,8,Fof the national minimum wage, or the
OL,9,Fnational living wage, which is what
OL,10,Fthe Government calls the minimum wage
OL,11,Ffor those aged over 21.
OL,13,FIn total, around 42,000 people have
OL,14,Fbeen repaid by their employers after
OL,15,Fbeing left out of pocket, the DBT said.
OL,17,FEG Group short-changed its workers the
OL,18,Fmost, according to the Government's
OL,19,Flatest investigation of pay between
OL,20,F2018 and 2023.
