OL,3,CHolland & Barrett and British Gas
OL,4,Cowner among firms fined for
OL,5,Cunderpaying staff
OL,7,FThe company, which was co-founded by
OL,8,Fthe billionaire Issa Brothers, but who
OL,9,Fhave since stepped back from leading
OL,10,Fthe firm, failed to pay #824,384 to
OL,11,F3,317 workers.
OL,13,FThis meant individual employees were
OL,14,Funderpaid about #250 on average.
OL,16,FThe company has significantly reduced
OL,17,Fthe size of its UK operations over the
OL,18,Fpast year, selling its UK petrol
OL,19,Fforecourts business and Cooplands
OL,20,Fbakeries. It still runs Starbucks
OL,21,Ffranchise stores across the UK.
