OL,7,FAnother in the top 10 was Centrica,
OL,8,Fwhich owns British Gas, having failed
OL,9,Fto pay #167,815 to 356 workers `
OL,10,Famounting to about #460 on average.
OL,12,FHigh street retailers Go Outdoors and
OL,13,FHolland & Barrett were also identified
OL,14,Fby the DBT in its latest naming round.
OL,16,FGo Outdoors was number seven on the
OL,17,Flist, owing #240,106 to 2,058 workers.
OL,19,FHolland & Barrett was ninth, having
OL,20,Ffailed to pay #153,079 to 2,551
OL,21,Femployees.
