OL,7,FThe national living wage was #11.44 in
OL,8,Fthe year to the end of March, and has
OL,9,Frisen to #12.21 since April.
OL,11,FThe minimum wage for 18-20-year-olds
OL,12,Frose to #10 this year, and for
OL,13,Fapprentices and those aged under 18 it
OL,14,Frose to #7.55.
OL,16,FThe DBT released a list of more than
OL,17,F500 employers in June that underpaid
OL,18,Fworkers between 2015 and 2022,
OL,19,Fincluding Pizza Express, Lidl and
OL,20,FBritish Airways.
