OL,7,FBusiness Secretary Peter Kyle said:
OL,8,F"Every worker deserves a fair day's
OL,9,Fpay for a fair day's work, and this
OL,10,Fgovernment will not tolerate rogue
OL,11,Femployers who short-change their staff.
OL,13,F"I know that no employer wants to end
OL,14,Fup on one of these lists. But our Plan
OL,15,Fto Make Work Pay cracks down on those
OL,16,Fnot playing by the rules."
