OL,7,FA spokeswoman for Holland & Barrett
OL,8,Fsaid: "Holland & Barrett has been
OL,9,Fnamed by the Government under the
OL,10,FNational Minimum Wage Naming Scheme,
OL,11,Ffollowing a historic issue dating back
OL,12,Fto 2015`2021 which was fully resolved
OL,13,Fin 2022.
OL,15,F"This was not a case of deliberate
OL,16,Funderpayment. The issue stemmed from
OL,17,Flegacy practices such as requiring
OL,18,Fteam members to wear specific shoes,
OL,19,Funpaid training completed at home, and
OL,20,Ftime spent preparing for shifts at our
OL,21,FBurton distribution site.
