OL,7,F"All arrears ` totalling around
OL,8,F#150,000 across the six-year period `
OL,9,Fwere repaid in full once identified,
OL,10,Fand we acted swiftly to upgrade
OL,11,Fprocesses and systems.
OL,13,F"While we respect the transparency of
OL,14,Fthe scheme, we are disappointed that
OL,15,Fnaming has occurred over three years
OL,16,Fafter the matter was settled."
OL,18,FEG Group, Centrica and Go Outdoors
OL,19,Fhave been contacted for comment.
